00:10.080 --> 00:15.133
...you have all these letters, these 26 letters jammed into this two-and-a-half-inch space,...

00:15.379 --> 00:17.755
...now you just have two buttons, you have a dot and a dash.

00:19.024 --> 00:19.852
All you have to do is this.

00:21.680 --> 00:22.133
It's amazing.

00:26.020 --> 00:27.150
You can tap it in the morning.

